	dprr:hasNoteText "Served under Dolabella, and at the end of the year lost to Brutus in Thessaly the cavalry he was bringing to his commander in Asia (Cic. Phil. 10.13, quaestor, cf. 11.27; Plut. Brut. 25.1, #)." .
